  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA physical status I or II undergoing endoscopic sinus surgery or septoplasty under
             balanced anesthesia with sevoflurane and remifentanil

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  predicted difficult airway, body mass index &gt; 30 kg/m2, history of obstructive sleep
             apnoea chronic respiratory disease or coughing, current smokers patients angiotensin
             converting enzyme-inhibitors
      </textblock>
